# Screenshots captured via /snap on the device.
# Copy from SD card /CardputerLLM/snaps/*.bmp into this folder; GitHub
# renders BMPs inline in markdown. Suggested filenames:
#
#   splash.bmp        cold-boot wordmark
#   empty.bmp         empty-state watermark + rotating tip
#   chat.bmp          a styled assistant reply
#   autocomplete.bmp  the slash command popup
#   menu.bmp          Fn+S menu
#   wifi.bmp          wifi scan list in the onboarding flow
